sfc: Replace TSOH_OFFSET with the equivalent NET_IP_ALIGN

If CONFIG_HAVE_EFFICIENT_UNALIGNED_ACCESS is defined then NET_IP_ALIGN
will be defined as 0, so this macro is redundant.

